title: For Sale:  1954 M48BO 8mm Mauser Unissued
postcontent: Up for sale is a gorgeous Unissued and unstamped 1954 Yugo Mauser, all matching numbers.  Includes sling, and Bayonet (the serials on the bayonet match the scabbard) and a pile of 253, yes I counted, 8mm Mauser rounds. I bought it from a collector a few months ago, i brought it to the range once and it ran flawlessly. Cool back story about this gun. Now you may be asking why there is no Yugoslavian Arsenal Stamp on it. Well, the yugoslavians were producing the  Mauser in the 50's and we're selling them to the highest bidders for contracts (even if the contracts were with warring parties) if the guns got  captured the Yugoslavians did not want the other parties to know they were supplying guns to whomever. This rifle came from a batch that was meant for a contract with Egypt, but the Egyptians never paid so they were crated up and put the market. $550 obo. Trades considered. Can do personal sale if wanted. If the right gun is offered in trade and makes me moist I can put money on top.
